@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<style>
    body {
        background-image: url('https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2016/11/19/13/06/matrix-1839237_960_720.jpg');
        background-size: cover;
        color: white;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 50px;
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    h1 {
        text-align: center;
    }

    p {
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
</style>

<div class="container">

    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p>
        Welcome to QuizMaster, your ultimate destination for creating, playing, and sharing quizzes on any topic imaginable! Whether you're a trivia enthusiast, an educator, or just looking for a fun way to challenge your friends, QuizMaster has something for everyone.
    </p>

    <p>
        With QuizMaster, you can unleash your creativity and craft engaging quizzes tailored to your interests. Create multiple-choice questions, add intriguing suggestions for responses, and customize your quizzes with unique themes and settings. Whether it's a pop culture quiz, a history trivia, or a science challenge, the possibilities are endless!
    </p>

    <p>
        But the excitement doesn't stop there. Once you've created your masterpiece, share it with the world and let others put their knowledge to the test. Challenge your friends, family, or even strangers from around the globe to see who reigns supreme as the QuizMaster!
    </p>

    <p>
        Not in the mood for creating? No problem! Dive into our vast collection of quizzes created by other users. From brain teasers to niche subjects, there's always something new to discover and learn.
    </p>

    <p>
        Track your progress, earn scores, and compete for the top spot on the leaderboards. With QuizMaster, every quiz is an adventure waiting to unfold. So what are you waiting for? Join the fun and become a QuizMaster today!
    </p>
</div>